reason.er.compositeObjects

Class Box<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • reason.er.compositeObjects.Box<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - generic
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ABox, TBox

    public abstract class Box<T,U>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class for Expression building code that constructs Boxes. Contains static variables that can control the types of Expressions that it produces. Boxes can normalize themselves.
    Author:
    Aaron Eberhart
